<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'SwapStyle | Thoughtful clothing exchange', stylesheet: '/home.css' }) %>
<body>
    <% const listingData = typeof colthList !== 'undefined' && Array.isArray(colthList) ? colthList : []; %>
    <% const featuredItems = listingData.slice(0, 4); %>
    <%- include('partials/navbar', { activePage: 'home' }) %>

    <main class="page-shell">
        <section class="container section">
            <div class="hero-panel hero-home">
                <div class="hero-grid">
                    <div class="hero-copy">
                        <span class="eyebrow">Circular fashion for everyday wardrobes</span>
                        <h1 class="display-title">Refresh your closet without the noise of fast fashion.</h1>
                        <p class="lead">
                            SwapStyle helps people exchange quality clothing through direct swaps and point-based redemption.
                            The experience is built to feel curated, trustworthy, and easy to return to.
                        </p>
                        <div class="actions">
                            <a href="/addClothes" class="btn btn-primary">List a piece</a>
                            <a href="/itemlisting" class="btn btn-secondary">Browse available items</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stats-row home-stats">
                            <div class="stats-card">
                                <span class="label">Live Listings</span>
                                <span class="value"><%= listingData.length %></span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stats-card">
                                <span class="label">Community Model</span>
                                <span class="value">Swap + Points</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stats-card">
                                <span class="label">Focus</span>
                                <span class="value">Reuse First</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hero-visual">
                        <div class="hero-gallery">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512436991641-6745cdb1723f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" class="hero-slide active" alt="Clothing rack">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503342217505-b0a15ec3261c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" class="hero-slide" alt="Fashion detail">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1469398715555-76331a6c7c9b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" class="hero-slide" alt="Folded clothing">
                        </div>
                        <div class="hero-note">
                            <span class="eyebrow">Why it works</span>
                            <p>Thoughtful product cards, clear condition details, and a calmer visual language make the platform feel more premium and dependable.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="container section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div>
                    <span class="eyebrow">Browse by use</span>
                    <h2>A cleaner way to explore inventory</h2>
                </div>
                <p>We softened the interface and grouped the marketplace around practical wardrobe moments so it feels closer to a boutique than a flashy marketplace.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="categories-grid">
                <article class="card category-card">
                    <div class="category-icon-wrap"><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i></div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3>Everyday Essentials</h3>
                        <p class="muted">Reliable basics, denim, knitwear, and versatile layers.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="card category-card">
                    <div class="category-icon-wrap"><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i></div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3>Polished Dressing</h3>
                        <p class="muted">Tailored pieces, office-ready looks, and occasion wear.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="card category-card">
                    <div class="category-icon-wrap"><i class="fas fa-person-walking"></i></div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3>Off-Duty Comfort</h3>
                        <p class="muted">Relaxed silhouettes, sportswear, and soft weekend staples.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="card category-card">
                    <div class="category-icon-wrap"><i class="fas fa-bag-shopping"></i></div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3>Accessories and Footwear</h3>
                        <p class="muted">The finishing details that keep wardrobes moving longer.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="container section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <div>
                    <span class="eyebrow">New arrivals</span>
                    <h2>Latest swappable pieces</h2>
                </div>
                <a href="/itemlisting" class="btn btn-outline">See full marketplace</a>
            </div>

            <div class="products-grid">
                <% if (featuredItems.length > 0) { %>
                    <% featuredItems.forEach(item => { %>
                        <article class="card product-card">
                            <div class="product-image">
                                <img src="<%= item.mainImageUrl %>" alt="<%= item.itemName %>">
                                <div class="overlay-chip"><%= item.condition || 'Ready to swap' %></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="product-info">
                                <span class="pill neutral"><%= item.category || 'Wardrobe staple' %></span>
                                <h3><%= item.itemName %></h3>
                                <p class="muted"><%= item.description ? item.description.slice(0, 90) : 'Thoughtfully listed by the SwapStyle community.' %><%= item.description && item.description.length > 90 ? '...' : '' %></p>
                                <div class="meta-row">
                                    <span>Size: <%= item.size || 'N/A' %></span>
                                    <span>Points: <%= item.points || 0 %></span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="price-line">
                                    <span class="price">$<%= item.price || 0 %></span>
                                    <a href="/itemlisting" class="btn-sm btn-secondary">View item</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                    <% }) %>
                <% } else { %>
                    <article class="card product-card">
                        <div class="product-image">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517841905240-472988babdf9?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Curated dress">
                            <div class="overlay-chip">Like new</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="product-info">
                            <span class="pill neutral">Womenswear</span>
                            <h3>Soft floral day dress</h3>
                            <p class="muted">A light example listing that shows how the calmer card treatment looks before community data fills in.</p>
                            <div class="meta-row">
                                <span>Size: M</span>
                                <span>Points: 180</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="price-line">
                                <span class="price">$18</span>
                                <a href="/itemlisting" class="btn-sm btn-secondary">Browse</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                    <article class="card product-card">
                        <div class="product-image">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521572163474-6864f9cf17ab?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Tailored jacket">
                            <div class="overlay-chip">Excellent</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="product-info">
                            <span class="pill neutral">Menswear</span>
                            <h3>Structured overshirt</h3>
                            <p class="muted">Neutral, editorial cards keep the marketplace professional without feeling cold or generic.</p>
                            <div class="meta-row">
                                <span>Size: L</span>
                                <span>Points: 240</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="price-line">
                                <span class="price">$24</span>
                                <a href="/itemlisting" class="btn-sm btn-secondary">Browse</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="container section">
            <div class="panel editorial-strip">
                <div>
                    <span class="eyebrow">How SwapStyle works</span>
                    <h2>Three simple steps to keep good clothing in circulation</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="editorial-steps">
                    <article class="step-card">
                        <span class="step-number">01</span>
                        <h3>List clearly</h3>
                        <p class="muted">Add sizing, condition, price, and a sharp photo so the next owner trusts the listing.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="step-card">
                        <span class="step-number">02</span>
                        <h3>Swap or redeem</h3>
                        <p class="muted">Choose direct exchange or use points to make the marketplace flexible for different shoppers.</p>
                    </article>
                    <article class="step-card">
                        <span class="step-number">03</span>
                        <h3>Repeat with ease</h3>
                        <p class="muted">A clearer dashboard and gentler UI make it easier to come back and participate regularly.</p>
                    </article>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </main>

    <div id="chatbot-fab" aria-label="Open chatbot" style="position:fixed;bottom:32px;right:32px;z-index:1000;background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-strong), var(--accent));color:#fdfaf4;width:60px;height:60px;display:grid;place-items:center;border-radius:50%;box-shadow:0 10px 25px rgba(65, 88, 70, 0.25);cursor:pointer;transition:transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;" onmouseenter="this.style.transform='scale(1.06) translateY(-2px)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 14px 30px rgba(65, 88, 70, 0.35)';" onmouseleave="this.style.transform='scale(1) translateY(0)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 10px 25px rgba(65, 88, 70, 0.25)';">
        <i class="fas fa-comments" style="font-size:24px;"></i>
    </div>

    <script src="/chatbot.js"></script>
    <script>

        const slides = document.querySelectorAll('.hero-slide');
        let currentSlide = 0;
        if (slides.length > 1) {
            setInterval(() => {
                slides[currentSlide].classList.remove('active');
                currentSlide = (currentSlide + 1) % slides.length;
                slides[currentSlide].classList.add('active');
            }, 3200);
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
